name: i dont belong here
description: For the past 15 years I've had this feeling, the feeling that I don't fit in, the feeling of being so different from others. I know we are all already different, but I somehow feel more different, not special just different. you might say being different is a good thing, but I'd say being different is like a disease that push everyone away from you.  It makes it difficult to connect with people, it makes you feel excluded, it makes you feel alone.
